title: Bushings
description: Maintenance activities for Bushings in DIST TRAFO system

body.raw:
# Bushings


## Visual

- Visual Inspect.
- Oil Level Check


## Electrical

- Ins. Resist.
- Power Factor Test


## Mechanical

- Tightness Check
- Sealing Test
